{"tid":2008387,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今次議會抗爭, 要集中焦點, 正名為「反國歌法抗爭」","createTime":"2020-05-09T04:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T15:58:36.000Z","uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dd7f5aa62c87a1ea1766e677884bda172ad0d7a2","tid":2008387,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:08:24.000Z","msg":"朋友既朋友既朋友話:<br />\n<br />\n- 單單突顯議事規則崩壞, 唔會吸引到最大的國際關注.<br />\n- 外國人最關注係惡法, 之後才會關注議事規則. &nbsp; 惡法才是焦點<br />\n<br />\n- 如果一件事既焦點唔吸引, 港共點破壞議事規則都無人理. &nbsp;<br />\n- 好似港共破壞議事規則dq劉小麗, 國際上無咩人理, 因為劉小麗慢讀宣誓跟本係own goal. (唔係想話dq劉小麗係公平.)<br />\n<br />\n- 如果想吸引國際關注, 就應該將「國歌法」放上焦點, 正名為「反國歌法抗爭」. 咁樣, 議會抗爭先會吸引多人關注<br />\n-  議事規則都重要, 但「國歌法」先會吸引較大關注.<br />\n<br />\n(當然, 「反國歌法抗爭」可以不只限於議會抗爭.)"},{"pid":"a63157bc214896082cc9699136e2939149385471","tid":2008387,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:08:32.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢有道理. <br />\n<br />\n另一方面, 美國「國歌法」都沒有法律刑罰.<br />\n要以西方的普世價值標準, 去反對「國歌法」.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1053140\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1053140&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d4nGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=cb44f846\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1053140&h=a30241a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1053140</a><br />\n<br />\n美國都有「國歌法」？<br />\n<br />\n葉國謙在電台節目上講「國歌法」。主持人提及在美國有黑人運動員在播國歌時拒絕站立以示抗議，繼而被譴責（其實就是被特朗普譴責）。葉國謙乘勢宣稱所有國家都有國歌法，如果有人偏偏要用如此方法抗議，就要承擔後果，受到處罰。<br />\n<br />\n究竟美國的「國歌法」是如何？正如圖示，就是說明當國歌奏起時，應該有何儀態，例如面向國旗之類。那麼如果拒絕做法律中所列應有儀態，最高刑罰是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n答案：無。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>對，是無罰則的。美國的「國歌法」只是指引，根本無罰則，因此任何人「違反」「國歌法」，不會受到任何法律制裁。</strong><br />\n<br />\n主持人胡亂引用例子，葉國謙胡說一通，企圖混淆視聽，實屬可恥。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「國歌法」是可以立的，明列國歌奏起時應該如何。但絕對不能有刑罰</strong>。現在北京建制陣營說要立為刑事法例，是直接奪取香港人的言論表達自由。我們必須反對到底。這與你是否大中華、自決派、本土派甚麼的統統無關。這是自由的底線。<br />\n<br />\n公民自由高於國家意識形態；<br />\n個人表達高於「民族大義」；<br />\n人民福祉高於愛國主義。<br />\n<br />\n在此聲明，不論最後立了怎樣的「國歌法」，本人以後聽到《中華人民共和國國歌》，絕不肅立。"},{"pid":"d5f1e16888719527ef236bc5622e8c96a1bb02ed","tid":2008387,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94699634fffe7d6ef40653bf8e017707484d52d","tid":2008387,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"戰略文無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80cbe187775fe5ca6abb2ec73550226b6b913f39","tid":2008387,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c88d14764a0ee32f6d764d09e2d9031afb3596","tid":2008387,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80cbe187775fe5ca6abb2ec73550226b6b913f39","tid":2008387,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4e0831b56b52bfb6854ead4b164097d01482a9","tid":2008387,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002f41d0ebc48b64cde86031acf3572658a6c309","tid":2008387,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"講到咁白會違宣誓?"},{"pid":"53ee05f6b045f52c118603e7b7c9c412b8847c76","tid":2008387,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"002f41d0ebc48b64cde86031acf3572658a6c309","tid":2008387,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"講到咁白會違宣誓?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:06:45.000Z","msg":"唔明。<br />\n<br />\n朋友既朋友， 只諗公關問題"},{"pid":"8c161a77eebf3000944b7ae410850ee4720eb334","tid":2008387,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"戰略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9e8ac1ceac1a1313d9844cd86d523a69657f86","tid":2008387,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a4e0b784fabb9c49b528ba71df236b5d083200","tid":2008387,"uid":273294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T15:58:36.000Z","msg":"同意。正名為「反國歌法」更能夠令外國人身同感受。"}]}